/*! @file
@brief README of the non-regression tests for features after converging wavefunctions

@page TESTS_DFT_POSTSCF Test the features after the self-consistent cycle
@brief Non-regression tests (features after the SCF)

Tests the features after converging the wavefunctions

The command <tt>make check</tt> performs the series of tests:
- @b Davidson-SiH4 Tests the Kohn-Sham eigenvalue calculation;
- @b TDDFT         Tests the Time-Dependent DFT calculation.

*/
